{"tid":514697,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[搵食]現實機師同你玩FSX","createTime":"2017-12-30T19:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T01:58:41.000Z","uid":164871,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e4113a64a85d29a0e4d1ccefaad2c9016ef6724e","tid":514697,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://aerosoft-shop.com/shop-rd/bilder/screenshots/simulatoren/fsx-se/fsx-se-08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faerosoft-shop.com%2Fshop-rd%2Fbilder%2Fscreenshots%2Fsimulatoren%2Ffsx-se%2Ffsx-se-08.jpg&h=2bce086f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的﹐小弟係個Multi-IFR rated CPL holder﹐閒時都會玩下FSX過下日辰﹐做下現實做唔到既野﹐Land下中環、taxiway﹐飛下青馬橋底咁。我打算搵人玩FSX（STEAM EDITION）﹐主要有幾個Target Groups﹐當然你唔係Group都可以PM我。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>想學模擬飛行、遲D會真係學飛</ins></strong>  <br />\n<br />\n想學模擬飛行﹐好多時你只可以靠睇攻略。不過﹐模擬飛行像真度咁高﹐如果你可以睇攻略就成為PRO既Virtual Pilot﹐咁CAD應該都可以靠筆試考曬CPL、ATPL個試。依家﹐我會同你係同一個Virtual Cockpit度教你做每一樣野﹐你唔再洗好似古人練功咁靠睇字學一樣要身體做既野。<br />\n<br />\n對於未來學飛既你﹐相信你都知學飛係幾貴架啦。單係機隨時都每小時1500、另外教練都要花幾百。如果你係SIM搵人同你練好﹐我唔會話同飛真機一樣感覺﹐但你都會學到八、九成。特別係IFR﹐唔操SIM而操真機﹐其實真係好蠢。<br />\n<br />\n同我一齊﹐我可以由VFR教到你去Multi-IFR﹐可以同你操In-flight Emergency、可以好似下圖既hihi ATC咁比少見既ATC Instruction 你。你現實唔想見既野﹐可以係安全無壓力既情況練熟先。<br />\n<br />\nPS︰如果你知識係0﹐我都可以Ground School﹐不過依樣係另外一樣野。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.quickmeme.com/img/36/36a72bc934d624fa10d5b3271c739181d47de9b6393192584df16e9bc7ecb4e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.quickmeme.com%2Fimg%2F36%2F36a72bc934d624fa10d5b3271c739181d47de9b6393192584df16e9bc7ecb4e0.jpg&h=7bdb429a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>已經係Pro Virtual Pilot﹐想挑戰自己</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n可能你已經日日打Virtual Airlines﹐行Approach熟過我。不過﹐你心有不甘﹐你唔肯定自己既Skill Set同真正既機長有無唔同。你搵我﹐我可以同你做模擬考試﹐咁你就可能得到CPL虛無既一句「你處理得好過真機師喎」（誤）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://braandcorsetsupplies.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/767495ab92732dac03084e8321ed69a2-star-quotes-good-quotes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbraandcorsetsupplies.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F767495ab92732dac03084e8321ed69a2-star-quotes-good-quotes.jpg&h=26b26c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>想學IFR、Flight Planning、Weather Briefing好多好多野呀</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n明既﹐一到IFR﹐飛行知識就會開始深。有時﹐你做到又唔一定做得岩﹐做得岩又未必做到好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.pexels.com/photos/46274/pexels-photo-46274.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.pexels.com%2Fphotos%2F46274%2Fpexels-photo-46274.jpeg&h=488efcdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>想打Mission﹐嬴到但想比人挑錯處</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n挑剔﹐係學習既一部份。你LAND到﹐就完左Mission﹐但現實世界某D方法係唔可以接受。電腦比你衝入RAMP﹐比你Low Lever Circuit 唔跟Missed Approach﹐但世界唔可以。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.pcaviator.com.au/store/images/D/SimpleFSXMissions-Volume3-PCAviator-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcaviator.com.au%2Fstore%2Fimages%2FD%2FSimpleFSXMissions-Volume3-PCAviator-4.jpg&h=ceabed76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左咁多﹐當然下面隨便吹水都可以﹐但我建議大家返大PO吹（我唔想玩小圈子分薄人）。<br />\n有興趣PM我﹐價錢睇Service同情況﹐但你最好齊Yoke、Rudder （最好有埋Throttle Set）﹐最少都要有個Stick或者Yoke。有得Trial<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"d523ae88b77a3fd878d2c5968480fb594c6332ee","tid":514697,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T19:56:02.000Z","msg":"唔係PM 係Telegram<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5b70775c36daeca82e3a9bfc18eaeb3535e08d","tid":514697,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T20:00:00.000Z","msg":"Tg: hkpilot.ca"},{"pid":"bdabb9ee9d47d85700151d440559174240ccb0e5","tid":514697,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c5b70775c36daeca82e3a9bfc18eaeb3535e08d","tid":514697,"uid":164871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T20:00:00.000Z","ms